title: South Park - Michael Jackson Special S08E07
description:
R.I.P. The King of Pop!

"The Jeffersons" is episode 117 of the Comedy Central animated series South Park. It was originally broadcast on April 21, 2004 and has been described as "a howlingly funny assault on Michael Jackson."[1] This is the second time in South Park history to feature Kenny speaking audible lines, as he is disguised as Blanket and not wearing his trademark parka.
